OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780319468
OL,3,CTributes paid to teenage boys killed
OL,4,Cin Newport crash
OL,6,FTributes have been paid following a
OL,7,Fcrash in Newport in which two teenage
OL,8,Fboys were killed.
OL,10,FJaydon Bowyer, 19, and Ta-Shay
OL,11,FCanoville, 16 died when their
OL,12,Fmotorbike collided with a BMW on
OL,13,FAberthaw Road on Thursday 7th May.
OL,15,FThe family of Ta-Shay Canoville
OL,16,Fdescribed him as someone 'whose life
OL,17,Ftouched so many hearts in ways words
OL,18,Fcan never express'
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
