OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780319468
OL,3,CTributes paid to teenage boys killed
OL,4,Cin Newport crash
OL,6,F'His smile could brighten even the
OL,7,Fdarkest day, and his presence made
OL,8,Flife better for everyone around him.
OL,10,F'Though his life was far too short,
OL,11,Fthe impact he made will last forever.'
OL,13,FThe familiy of Jaydon Bowyer described
OL,14,Fhim as ' a truly adored member of the
OL,15,Fcommunity ` a young man no one ever
OL,16,Fhad a bad word to say about'
OL,18,F'Jaydon was polite, respectful, and
OL,19,Ffull of cheeky charm.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
