OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780319468
OL,3,CTributes paid to teenage boys killed
OL,4,Cin Newport crash
OL,6,F'Jaydon had a way of lighting up every
OL,7,Froom he walked into, with his handsome
OL,8,Fface and that unforgettable
OL,9,Fmischievous smile.
OL,11,F'He brought warmth, laughter, and
OL,12,Fenergy wherever he went.'
OL,14,FTerell Case, 18, of Sandpiper Way,
OL,15,FDuffryn, and Joshua Williams, 34, of
OL,16,Fno fixed abode, are both due back in
OL,17,Fcourt next month both charged with two
OL,18,Fcounts of murder.
